News Releases, Media Advisories

November 24, 2003

ATTENTION WIRE SERVICES, DAYBOOK EDITORS:
FINAL AUDIT REPORT ON
MISSOURI DEMOCRATIC STATE COMMITTEE
The Federal Election Commission has made available the final report on the Missouri Democratic State Committee. This audit covers the period of January 1, 1999 through December 31, 2000.

Contact: FEC Press Office (202) 694-1220, 999 E Street NW
title: Final Audit Report on Missouri Democratic State Committee is Available
